Description:
The pet lover’s favorite! When you purchase this listing we will design a fully customized pet portrait based off the image(s) you provide and add it to a pillow.
Snuggle up to your furbaby with this adorable pillow featuring exclusive art from Design My Dog™. If you’re looking for unique pet lover gifts, you’ve come to the right spot! Our throw pillows make great gifts for pet lovers.
With 16 colors to choose from, these colorful pillows can match any decor. Our custom pillows are manufactured from high quality spun polyester and printed in the USA. The design is printed on both sides and a fluffy pillow insert is included when you select the "pillow" option (insert is not included when you select the "case" option). These decorative pillows make perfect accent pillows for pet lovers! Each pillow is made to order and includes a 100% quality guarantee.
❤ Two Pet Option
If you choose two pets, one pet will be printed on each side of the pillow.
❤ How It Works
Step 1 – Select the size and color of the pillow you would like to purchase and submit your order. 
Step 2 – After purchasing, send us a message via Etsy Conversation with your reference photo(s) and the breed/species of your pet.
Step 3 – Once we’ve received your photo(s), a proof will be sent via Etsy conversation within 10 business days.  At that time, you can approve the design or request changes. If you would prefer your proof to be sent via email just include your email address. 
Step 4 – After the design is approved your custom pillow will ship in 2-6 business days.
❤ Add Products
You can add addtional products with our Add/Re-order listings: 
https://www.etsy.com/shop/DesignMyDog?&section_id=20400290
❤ Photo Guide (www.designmydog.com/photo-guide)
- Photo should be well lit and show the true color of your pet
- We should be able to see the shape of the neck and shoulders
- Camera should be directly in front of your pet
- Pet should be looking directly at the camera
- Make sure your pet has a good facial expression so we can capture their personality
- If you send multiple photos be sure to explain what you like about each photo
❤ Product Highlights
- Hand drawn custom pet illustration (not a filter)
- Available in 2 sizes
- Available in 16 colors
- Available with or without pillow insert
- Pillow option includes pillow insert
- Case option does not include pillow insert
- Manufactured and printed in the USA
- Made from high quality spun polyester
- Concealed zipper cover
- Design printed on both sides
- Machine washable
- 100% quality guarantee
- Made to order just for you
- Free shipping to the US
❤ Important Info
- We can design any animal as long as you provide a good reference photo. See our photo guide for photo requirements  (designmydog.com/photo-guide).
- If a good reference photo cannot be provided we will refund your order.
- The design will include your pet's face and upper body only. Please message us for a quote if you would like a full body design.
- This listing includes a one time, custom design fee. If you ever wish to purchase more products with the design you will not have to pay the fee again.
- You can order additional items with the custom pet design at any time using our Add-On/Re-Order Products 
https://www.etsy.com/shop/DesignMyDog?&section_id=20400290.
- Be sure to check out our Custom Design Gallery to see other custom pet designs we have done (designmydog.com/custom-design-gallery).
- If changes are requested based on new photos additional charges may apply.
- All designs remain property of Design My Dog™.

Description:
Looking for an affordable, custom logo to help brand your business? Whether you're just getting started or doing some rebranding, I'm here to offer personalized graphic design to make your business pop. Be it a modern logo, watercolor logo, professional logo or something more traditional or glittery, I'll make it happen. I won't stop designing until you're happy!
.............................................................................
IT'S GIVEAWAY TIME!
Every logo purchase made between now and April 30th will go into a drawing to win a full refund! Winners will be emailed an announced on social media (first name only) on May 2nd.
.............................................................................
Included in your purchase is:
MY TIME.
After talking with you about what you'd like, I'll present you with a custom design. After receiving this proof, you are allowed an unlimited number of modifications until you receive your final files.
PNG and JPEG FILES.
You'll receive your logo as a PNG (transparent background) image and a JPEG. If you need your file saved in other formats, I can do that, too. Vector files provided upon request.
TWO LOGO LAYOUTS OF YOUR CHOICE.
Maybe you want a horizontal and vertical version or a FB banner and cover photo, or maybe you need an Etsy banner and traditional logo. You choose which two canvases you need filled, and I'll rearrange your logo to make it stand out in the settings you've chosen.
If this listing doesn't quite fit your needs, please contact me. I'm happy to sub out options or create add-ons to make this bundle work for you! 
Want to see examples of my work? I'm happy to send you some examples, or you may look around my Etsy shop to see examples of my work. Please know that I'm working in Photoshop, so color, font, and imagery options are pretty endless. I will only use fonts and images that are approved for commercial use. 
Please contact me with your desired time frame for receiving your first proof if you need it sooner than my listed turnaround time (shown under "Shipping & Policies").  The time in which you receive your proof is dependent on my work load. Please pay close attention to the turnaround time associated with this item. If you’d like to rush your processing and move your order to the top of my queue, please add this rush listing to your cart: 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/255837153/rush-my-order-processing-time-only.
 
Please contact me with any questions. I look forward to working with you!

The SettonBrothers Laptop bag, allows you to transport your laptop with an executive look and a sleek design. The case provides maximum protection. Convenient, comfortable, and easy to carry, the SettonBrothers Laptop; Tablet Bag is a slim shoulder bag designed protect and transport to your electronics. 
FEATURES: 
. Crafted with Vegan leather and luxurious cotton fabric. 
. Complete notebook protection 
. modern and unique designed by SettonBrothers
. This item is brand new direct from the Manufacturer
. Setton Brothers is the only authorized seller of this product
. All/any other products that are sold are counterfeit.
Dimension: 15"x12.5"x3"
CRAFTSMANSHIP
Because of our commitment to a full vegan line of products, we are constantly seeking innovative ways to provide products made from quality leather alternatives.
Through careful partnerships with like-minded manufacturers, we source gorgeous materials and hardware from around the world. Our collections are characterized by meticulous attention to detail and exceptional craftsmanship that make all the difference.
STYLE
With Argentinian roots and a New York sensibility, we design bags made with the city dweller in mind.
Both durable and stylish, the Setton Brothers’ refined simplicity will suit your style and life.
With quality that was once reserved for the most expensive luxury brands, Setton Brothers makes gorgeous men’s bags accessible to all.
HUMANITY
We are a vegetarian company committed to operating a business that respects the planet as well as the people and animals on it.
We believe that no animal should give their life for the sake of fashion and do not use leather, skins or furs in any of our products.
 Most people are led to believe that leather is a byproduct of the meat industry, that it’s simply a "leftover," and if we don’t use it, it will go to waste. This is a common misconception. The truth is that leather is not a byproduct of meat and is not produced in an effort to minimize waste. In fact, much of the leather sold comes from animals killed primarily for their skins, and is produced because it is a highly profitable and lucrative business.
A cow’s skin is approximately 10% of her total value, making it the most profitable part of her body. Surprisingly, leather actually makes the meat industry more sustainable, as use of animals skins makes raising animals more profitable than meat alone could.
THE ENVIRONMENT
The leather industry has a considerable negative impact on the environment, making up a significant percentage of manmade greenhouse gas emissions and polluting ground water near leather tanneries with known carcinogens, lead and formaldehyde.
SettonBrothers is proud to be producing products that are kinder to the environment.
We keep strict environmental standards, abiding by the safest industry regulations and manufacturing without PVCs.

About this item:
---------------------------------------------------
The Batman version of our 3D printed spinner style fidget toy is perfect for those who focus better while fidgeting with something. Featuring 3 bearings that allow the toy to be spun from any bearing point. Placing a pencil through the middle bearing will allow it to be spun easily around the center point. 
These fidget toys are great for kids who have trouble holding still. For children (or adults) with ADHD, being "distracted" by the toy can allow them to better focus on the important things going on around them. Great for use during school, church, movies, car trips, etc. 
Includes fingers caps for the center bearing.
• No Bearings version (previously called "Frame & Caps Only") is just what it sounds like - a frame and caps, but no bearings.  The spinner cannot spin without bearings, this option if for those people planning to add their own. Please see photo example.
• Steel bearings are lower quality but still spin fairly well
• Hybrid Ceramic bearings spin longer than Steel and offer a smoother feeling spin.  This option includes a Hybrid Ceramic bearing in the center spot only, outside bearings are Steel.
Made of PLA plastic, printed at 0.2mm print quality resolution. Measures 3" at widest point. Bearing colors may vary.
